phrases: I cannot help but follow Sugawara-kun with my eyes these days.
Are you in love or something?
I do not know much about love and stuff.
But do not you want to when you see everyone else?
Hey, we were just talking about you, Ayaka-chan.
Ayaka-chan, how did you start going out with Goda-kun?
Do not you want to know, too, Chii-chan?
O-Oh, yeah, I was just looking for Sensei.
Cannot we talk just a little?
Well, if it is just a little...
Come on, are not you curious, Chii-chan?
You are interested, are not you?
Is there someone you like, Chii-chan?
She is been sighing nonstop lately.
Oh, I was like that, too, though.
That is what happens when you like someone.
There is not really anyone I like.
I would follow Goda-kun with my eyes unconsciously,
or think about him without realizing it.
I was pretty out of it during club work, too.
Come on, Chii-chan, is there seriously no one you like?
Besides, why would you guess Sugawara-kun?
Oh, no, it is just a rumor that I heard.
I have heard that rumor, too.
It is just a rumor, though.
But maybe if you confessed to him...
I-I am not going to, no way.
By the way, how did you confess, Ayaka-chan?
Because he gave the weirdest first kiss ever.
I do agree he messed up, but are you sure you really want to break up?
I think I will stop messaging her.
It is not like Chiaki was trying to be awful.
If she does not reply after one more message, I will give up.
If he apologizes one more time, I will forgive him.
I am really sorry about what happened.
I will not try to pull weird kisses anymore.
He is been messaging me every day.
Yeah, this is the best way to do it.
I want to apologize directly if I can.
She does not leave her phone even when she takes a bath.
I am sure he was apologizing again.
I just need to reply tomorrow.
I guess I will give up.
But what if Chiaki gives up?
After how long I have ignored him, he might just quit.
He might even hate me now.
I do not want him to hate me.
He pisses me off sometimes, but I love him.
I want to apologize to him.
Kana, are you ever coming out?
I dropped my phone in the bath.
Just give it a good whack.
What if it gets even worse?
He has not given up yet!
Fine, I am blocking you, too, idiot!
That is the problem with technology!
Did I forget my pencil leads?
If I gave her my pencil leads, would she think I had ulterior motives?
If I asked Takase instead of my girl friends,
for a pencil lead, would he think I had ulterior motives?
Well, I mean, I do have an ulterior motive.
Yuki-chan, can I have some pencil leads?
Sorry, my pencil leads are 0.4 millimeter.
Why do not you ask Takase-kun?
It is your chance to get close to him.
No, do not bring that up!
Crap, I am already out of lead.
Pass your answer sheets towards the front.
I will give you mine sometime.
Why are not they going out?
The solution of ax = b is...
You want to go to college?
You are already in third year.
Is not it too late to start studying now?
Th-That is why I am studying now!
We do not have money, though.
Going to college is one thing, but private?
That is what I said to my mom,
but am I really going to make it into public college, studying now?
I skipped or slept through all my exams until now.
everyone else looks better than me.
I think I really did start too late.
She is awoken to the fact that exams are approaching.
You could learn from her, Kyouko-san
I mean, is not she dating the student council president?
Are not you going to talk to her?
It is part of her practice.
She will be alone at the exam.
You say that, but you are the one who is trying not to freak out.
Remember what you learned with Akagi!
Can I kiss you when you are done?
Fundamentals of Exam Problems Mathematics III
I think I answered it, but...
I reviewed it over and over.
I am going to get this right and go to college with Akagi.
What do you do in these situations again?
I am weird if I raise my hand?
There is a delinquent taking the exams.
She is trying to go to college.
It does not matter how hard I try.
Sensei, could you please pick up this eraser?
I see you are working hard this time.
I am rooting for you, too.
Want to go to the nurse's office?
I want to nap in the nurse's office, Sensei.
